    The Profit
  



Looking to grow your business? CNBC, Executive Producer Amber Mazzola, and Machete Productions can provide you with what you need to save or grow your business. 
Apply now for a chance to save your business!
Marcus Lemonis, who has been called America’s number one business turnaround artist, is on the hunt for struggling businesses that are desperate for cash and ripe for a deal. In the last 10 years, he has successfully turned around over 100 companies, and now he’s bringing those skills to CNBC by putting his own money directly into the failing businesses.
