Car Makes & Models












Q:
Can you put scissor doors on a Ferrari?


A:
Yes, scissor doors, also known as Lambo doors, can be put on a Ferrari using an after-market kit. Such a kit may include special hinges that will replace the factory-installed Ferrari hinges.


See Full Answer

