Car Makes & Models












Q:
What size rims can you put on Ferrari cars?


A:
What size rims an owner should put on a stock Ferrari depends on the year and model of the vehicle. If the Ferrari has been customized, or if the owner wants to deviate from recommended rims, the rim may also drastically affect performance.


